OL,3,CSecond person dies after road tunnel
OL,4,Ccollision
OL,6,FA second person has died after two
OL,7,Fcars collided near the Hindhead Tunnel
OL,8,Fon the A3 in Surrey.
OL,10,FThe crash happened just before 6.30pm
OL,11,Fon Tuesday, March 3rd.
OL,13,FThe driver of one car, a man in his
OL,14,F20s, died at the scene, according to
OL,15,Fofficers.
OL,17,FA woman in her thirties, the driver of
OL,18,Fthe second vehicle, was taken to
OL,19,Fhospital with life-threatening
OL,20,Finjuries and has now sadly died in
OL,21,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
