PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1772989874
OL,3,CSecond person dies after road tunnel
OL,4,Ccollision
OL,6,FAfter exiting the tunnel, the vehicle
OL,7,Fcrossed the central reservation onto
OL,8,Fthe southbound carriageway, where it
OL,9,Fhas collided with the grey Fiesta.
OL,11,FOfficers sy they're looking for any
OL,12,Finformation that can explain why this
OL,13,Fhappened and the moments leading up to
OL,14,Fthe collision.
OL,16,FThey've asked anyone who witnessed the
OL,17,Fcollision, or either vehicle prior to
OL,18,Fthe crash, to contact them.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
